<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-32">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-100 mb-8">
        Standards &amp; coverage
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Anchored in standards</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-zinc-400 text-sm">
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                    <span>RFC 8707 audience binding &amp; multi-issuer trust</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                    <span>RFC 9728 protected-resource metadata</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                    <span>Per-tenant tool-schema pinning</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                    <span>SIEM export: CEF, LEEF, JSONL, Syslog (RFC 5424)</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                    <span class="text-emerald-400 mt-1">&#x2022;</span>
                    <span>OTLP trace/audit-span export</span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/40 p-6">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">OWASP MCP Top 10</h3>
            <p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">
                Mapped against the OWASP MCP Top 10 &mdash; including what Hangar
                deliberately does not cover. It does not parse prompt semantics:
                MCP05/06/10 are out of scope by design. An enforcement plane enforces
                policy; it does not guess intent.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
